            . I live in <placeName id="t18280911-146-crimeloc750">Barbican</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-146-crimeloc750" type="placeName" value="Barbican"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280911-146-crimeloc750" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-146-off749 t18280911-146-crimeloc750"></join>. On Wednesday, the <rs id="t18280911-146-cd751" type="crimeDate">20th of August</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-146-off749 t18280911-146-cd751"></join>, between eight and nine o'clock in the evening, the prisoner came into my shop, and asked for a cotton handkerchief, which came to 1s. - he threw down a 5s. piece; I looked at it, and threw it down, saying it was bad; he said "Bad, why I have just taken it" - I had taken one just before, and told him to let me look at it again; he said No - he would go and get it changed - I jumped over the counter, and detained him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-146-person882">
                  JOHN 
                  HARRISON
               <interp inst="t18280911-146-person882" type="surname" value="HARRISON"></interp>
