                     <interp inst="t18280911-146-person882" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I searched the prisoner, and found this 5s. piece on him.</p>
               <p>MR. FIELD. I am an inspector of coin. Both these 5s. pieces are counterfeit - both of the same description, and from the same mould.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was selling things, and took them.</p>
